    title: "Why Your Loan Calculator Gives Different Results (Explained)",
    description: "Understand why different loan calculators show different monthly payments and total interest. Learn about amortization methods, fee inclusion, and rounding.",
    difficulty: "advanced",
    category: "finance",
    toolSlugs: ["loan-calculator", "mortgage-calculator", "compound-interest-calculator"],
